data.description: Welcome to 459 Dickson Hill Circle! This beautiful 6-bedroom, 3.5-bath home w/ walk-out basement is move-in ready.  It features fresh paint, hardwood floors throughout the main level and crown and box molding to give it a custom feel. The living room is large and creates an open space with plenty of natural light. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, including a gas cooktop, granite countertops and tile backsplash. The main floor also includes a bedroom with a full bath, offering a perfect space for guests or a home office. The primary bedroom is located on the 2nd level of the home and features two walk-in closets and a sitting room that provides a great space for a home library or reading nook. Three additional bedrooms and another full bath complete the upper level, providing ample room for family and guests. The fully finished walk-out basement is a true highlight of this home. A large open living room with a fireplace creates a perfect place for movie nights or entertaining friends. The dry bar/kitchen area adds convenience, while an additional bedroom and half bath offer flexibility and extra space. For those focused on health and fitness, the basement also includes an exercise room, making staying active a breeze. This home is located in Parrish Plantation which features a community pool and playground. Don't miss the opportunity to call this beautiful property home – check out the 3d tour and schedule your showing today!
